```cs
using System;

public interface Up<U>
{
    void Bar(U i);
    void Bar(int i);
}

public interface Down<U>
{
    void Bar(int i);
    void Bar(U i);
}

public class Foo : Up<int>, Down<int> 
{
    void Up<int>.Bar(int i) { Console.Write("0"); }
    void Down<int>.Bar(int i) { Console.Write("1"); }
    public void Bar(int i) { Console.Write("2"); }
}

class Program
{
    static void Main()
    {
        Foo foo = new Foo();
        ((Up<int>)foo).Bar(0);
        ((Down<int>)foo).Bar(0);
    }
}
```
